Context: The George Brown College Foundation acknowledged donors who gave leading gifts of $100,000 or more and annual gifts of $10,000 or more between April 1, 2019, and March 31, 2020. During this period, George Brown College launched a new strategic plan named "Imagining Possibilities: Vision 2030/Strategy 2022." This plan introduced new partnerships, state-of-the-art learning and research facilities, and innovative ways of teaching and learning throughout the academic year 2019-2020. The contact details for the college are: phone number 416-415-2000, TTY 1-877-515-5559, email ask.george@georgebrown.ca. Interested individuals can sign up to receive application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more via the website. The information on the website is subject to change without notice.
